<br>
The twist is that the Lizards are an ancient race, and they've developed technology very slowly and gradually at a predictable rate, no 'spurts' of innovation as on Earth.  The Lizards have conquered 2 other planets and these two seperate species had also developed technology the same way as the Lizards... slowly.  So when the alien invasion relied on 700 year old surveilance information from a probe sent to Earth, they expected to see the same level of technology... sword weilding brutes on horseback!  But when the aliens arrived the entire planet was armed with mechanized weapons!<br>
<br>
Of course, the first thing the invasion leader does is to order the high altitude nuclear bursts over major cities around the globe... the EMP used to knock out communications and to disable vehicles... doesn't work.<br>
<br>
